heading: Belfry Zakara Dungeon Guide
content: Belfry Zakara does not host any dangerous monsters besides Skeleton Ballistas, and features a compact layout that requires minor backtracking. It is solid for farming, but is not currently a possible . Drowned Seahag is an easy meat piñata boss with only one annoying knockback attack. This dungeon unlocks the , an excellent offensive aspect for the Druid. While every dungeon has a somewhat randomized layout, there are patterns to where objectives and bosses are located. This map will help you identify those layouts so you can complete dungeons faster and maximize your XP and loot per hour! Reviewed by
